  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Category: Clan</p>\n<p>Prerequisite: Kaguya Clan, Level 4+</p>\n<p>Through many battles, you have developed strategies to overwhelm your enemies with frightening accuracy. <br />You gain the following Benefits:</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>• Increase your Strength or Dexterity score by 1, to a maximum of 20. </p>\n<p><br />• You can gain advantage on a Kaguya clan Hijutsu's attack if you are targeting a creature who has targeted you within the last round. <br />You can gain advantage in this way twice per rest. </p>\n<p><br />• When you make a melee weapon attack against a creature where your attack result is 5 higher than the target AC, on a successful hit where you deal damage, you reduce the targets speed by half, until the end of their next turn. </p>\n<p><br />• You have learned to maneuver in a way that increases your combat range. <br />All attacks made with your Bone Weapons gain the Reach property. <br />If the weapon already has the Reach property, it instead gains a second rank of Reach.</p>",
